This paper focuses on fairness-aware learning and discrimination prevention in data mining, which are core topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The proposed method, FairGAN, is a type of generative adversarial network (GAN), which is a popular technique in computer vision (cs.CV) and has also been applied in security and privacy (cs.CR) and social impact (cs.SI) research. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
